
! Overrides for Regolith settings!
!
! To deploy them use `regolith-look refresh`
! If the changes fail to load, ensure that `~/.config/regolith2/Xresources` is
! symlinked to this file.
!
! See reglotih-look-default root resources for an overviiew of keys
! https://github.com/regolith-linux/regolith-look-default/blob/286e055f0710cbd5cab8732200bc3441771be99f/usr/share/regolith-look/default/root

! Regolith-look configuration
! This field is auto-updated when running `regolith-look set ...`
regolith.look.path: /usr/share/regolith-look/ayu-mirage

! Give workspaces nice names
! Each regolith theme can use a different font, This is described in
! /usr/share/regolith-look/THEME-NAME/root in the `gtk.font_name` option.
!
! The icons here come from https://www.nerdfonts.com/cheat-sheet
! (The ayu theme uses nerd fonts).
!
! Note: workspace icons are only updated when a workspace is created.
!
! To see the icons in the browser, add `Hack Nerd Font` to the list of editor
! fonts.

